<bug no-bug="" comments="">
    <id>1671</id>
    <title ob="x" eb="" sr="">extra &lt;searchpath&gt; added every time project is saved</title>
    <desc>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="1">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="1.1">Testcase:</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="2">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="2.1">1 start argouml 0.13.2</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="2.2">2 create a class and name it 'A'</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="2.3">3 create an attr '[IDENTIFIER]' by doubleclicking in the attr compartment</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="2.4">4 create an oper by doubleclicking in the attr compartment</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="2.5">5 save project as '[IDENTIFIER]'</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="2.6">6 make a copy of [IDENTIFIER]</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="2.7">7 make new project (important!)</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="2.8">8 open [IDENTIFIER]</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="2.9">9 save</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="3">
            <st ob="" eb="x" sr="" id="3.1">Theoretically, the two .</st>
            <st ob="" eb="x" sr="" id="3.2">zargo files should be identically since there
were made no changes.</st>
            <st ob="x" eb="" sr="" id="3.3">The following analysis reveals differences in the 5 files contained in
the zip file [IDENTIFIER].</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="3.4">These differences should be fixed, because
they will affect the files iteratively at every save/load cycle.</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="3.5">(The test case is very simple.</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="3.6">Ideally, the analysis should be done
with a project that has all diagram types and all cases in it.)</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="4">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="4.1">1 [IDENTIFIER]</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="5">
            <st ob="x" eb="" sr="" id="5.1">The line
  &lt;searchpath href="PROJECT_DIR" /&gt;
was added.</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="6">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="6.1">2 [IDENTIFIER]</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="7">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="7.1">OK, identical</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="8">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="8.1">3 [IDENTIFIER]</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="9">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="9.1">OK, identical</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="10">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="10.1">4 test_ClassDiagram1.</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="10.2">pgml</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="11">
            <st ob="x" eb="" sr="" id="11.1">a strange empty [IDENTIFIER] is added:
  &lt;group name="Fig1"
       description="[IDENTIFIER][0, 0, 0, 0]"
       fill="1"
       fillcolor="-1"
       stroke="1"
       strokecolor="-16777216"
  &gt;
    &lt;private&gt;
    &lt;/private&gt;
    
  &lt;/group&gt;</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="12">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="12.1">5 test_UsecaseDiagram1.</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="12.2">pgml</st>
        </parg>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="13">
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="13.1">OK, identical (of course, it was empty)</st>
        </parg>
    </desc>
